README:
## Description
We scanned an independent cohort of participants to address the effects of ketones on brain function. The scans involved three conditions:  (1) Fasting:  following their standard diet, with an overnight fast (both sessions, run-1); (2) Glucose Bolus:  breaking the fast with a glucose drink (Glucose Tolerance Test Beverages, Fisher Scientific, Inc.; Hampton NH) (ses-glc_run-2); and (3) D-Î²Hb Ketone Ester Bolus: breaking the fast with a ketone drink (D-Î²-hydroxybutyrate ketone ester; HVMN, San Francisco CA) (ses-bhb_run-2). The D-Î²Hb ketone ester was weight-dosed for each participant at 395mg/kg. For more details, see our article referenced below.
